"Xiera":
"You've defeated the Devil Castle!
We may have managed this time, but who knows what our outcome will be later!"

"Devil Castles that appear in Buster Quests
will not be defeated even if you destroy
their cores.

You must destroy their heads to defeat them.

Powerful Demons will spawn and attack, as
well as powerful attacks from the Devil Castle.

Defeat the Devil Castle and seize your victory!"
